#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:15
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/text"
msgstr "看起来你已经在海盗船进入小行星带以躲避探测时找到了它们。你可以趁它们溜走之前追上去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:19
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "在他们之后！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:21
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "时间紧迫，你立即与他们交战。小心别损坏货物！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:24
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:30
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/text"
msgstr "（海盗声望 1 级以上）向他们喊话，提出直接买下货物。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:32
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/text"
msgstr "海盗们还没撬开那件货物。他们寻思着，与其赌货物里有什么，不如先稳赚一笔废料，于是接受了你的出价。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:37
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:39
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "现在你需要做出一个选择。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:41
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "联系吸虫族，告知他们工作已经完成。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:43
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"太好了！共和国非常感谢你。只是...不要告诉任何人这件事。在整个星联的事情上，这个协议是有点非法的，但我真的没有精力去杀你。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:46
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:52
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "将货物窃为己有。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:54
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你打开了货物，发现里面有一架无人机。你很满意并愿意背叛吸虫族，你抢到了它并准备离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:57
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[@req=\"rep_pirate\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append:67
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_asteroid.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ASTEROID_TRANSPORT_PIRATES\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "那就别管货物了，我们走吧。"
